Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Assassinations committee
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjn70
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Nov 1976
New House select committee to investigate evidence in Kennedy and Luther King assassinations. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less